I would also like you to swap Vesktop for Discord with Vencord enabaled with the following override:

```nix
    (discord.override {
      # withOpenASAR = true; # can do this here too
      withVencord = true;
    })
```

Place this in a new file in the @lib/users/brojo/programs/ directory named `discord.nix` and include it in the @lib/users/brojo/home.nix imports.

